<BR>
Luclin
<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=32057">Magelo profile</a><BR>
"It's not paranoia if they really ARE out to get me..."</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umappill.showPublicProfile?language=EN>mappill</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/12/01 3:01:23 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New spells</span><hr size=1> Aye, <br>
PoTG + BoF + Nalt Mark &gt; Aego <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uulicia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ulicia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/13/01 1:28:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New spells</span><hr size=1> Correction: the portal that takes you to the vendor who sells druid spells is NEITHER in an out-of-the-way place, NOR is it in a domed building. It's in a rather large, open-roofed, SQUARE building that's not very far from anything. The portal is in the back of the room; in the front stand several barbarians, most of whom sell ingredients for shaman potions. I don't want to think about how much wasted time I just spend trying to find this vendor based on that description... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umilwein.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milwein</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/13/01 4:20:16 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://photos.netclubs.com/live/photos/photocenter/g/o/e/4/e49htrv4pra139ke0188nko3i4/milpic.jpg HEIGHT=200 WIDTH=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New spells</span><hr size=1> BTW, the way out of the place with the spells is by clicking the tree in the middle of the room.<br>
<br>
I got to feel stupid when I first went there so you don't have to :) <p><left><font face=arial color=black size=2><b> <BR><A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=4918">Milwein Fenrir</A>
